<chapter id="crunchyfrog-introduction" lang="en" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
	<title>Introduction</title>
	<para>
		<application>CrunchyFrog</application> is a database navigator
		and query tool for GNOME.
		Currently the following databases are supported:
	</para>
	<itemizedlist>
		<listitem><para>PostgreSQL</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>MySQL</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>SQLite3</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>Oracle</para></listitem>
		<listitem><para>LDAP</para></listitem>
	</itemizedlist>
	<para>
		<application>CrunchyFrog</application> can be extended using
		plugins.
	</para>
</chapter>